<section class="ds-section" id="copywriting">
  <div class="ds-wrapper">
    <div class="ds-label">06 — Copywriting</div>
    <h2 class="ds-section-title">Headline & Hook Guide</h2>
    <p class="ds-section-desc">The headline is the product. 80% of people read the headline and nothing else. Every surface — landing page, deck slide, video thumbnail, ad — must hook in the first line.</p>

    <!-- Formula -->
    <div class="ds-card-dark" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-8)">
      <div class="ds-label" style="color:var(--blue-400);margin-bottom:var(--space-4)">The Aavishkar Headline Formula</div>
      <div style="font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:var(--space-6)">
        [Pain / Outcome] +<br>
        [Time or Contrast] +<br>
        [Implied Action]
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:var(--text-base);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);line-height:1.7">
        Lead with what the user loses or gains. Add a time or contrast signal that makes it feel urgent or surprising. 
        Imply what they need to do next — don't explain, don't hedge.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Good vs Bad -->
    <div class="hook-card">
      <div class="hook-header">
        <span style="font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-700)">easemyreco — Tally Reconciliation</span>
        <div class="ds-flex" style="gap:var(--space-3)">
          <span class="hook-bad">✗ WEAK</span>
          <span class="hook-good">✓ STRONG</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hook-headline">
        <div class="ds-grid-2">
          <div style="padding:var(--space-6);background:#FEF2F2;border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
            <div style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-error);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:var(--space-3)">✗ Weak headline</div>
            <p style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);line-height:1.2">Tally Ledger Reconciliation Tool for Businesses</p>
            <p style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-400);margin-top:var(--space-3)">Describes the product. Says nothing about the user's pain.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:var(--space-6);background:#F0FDF4;border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
            <div style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-success);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:var(--space-3)">✓ Strong headline</div>
            <p style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Stop losing hours to reco.<br><em style="color:var(--blue-600);font-style:normal">Find every mismatch in minutes.</em></p>
            <p style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-400);margin-top:var(--space-3)">Pain + contrast + implied speed. Instantly clear what you gain.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hook-card" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-8)">
      <div class="hook-header">
        <span style="font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-700)">Generic product — More examples</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hook-headline">
        <div class="ds-stack">
          <div style="padding:var(--space-5);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
            <p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--blue-600);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">Pattern: Outcome + Speed</p>
            <p style="font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Your vendor data.<br><span style="color:var(--blue-600)">Organised in 60 seconds.</span></p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:var(--space-5);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
            <p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--blue-600);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">Pattern: Before → After</p>
            <p style="font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Spreadsheet chaos.<br><span style="color:var(--blue-600)">One click to clarity.</span></p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:var(--space-5);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg)">
            <p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--blue-600);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">Pattern: The Insult</p>
            <p style="font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Your competitors already<br><span style="color:var(--blue-600)">automated this.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rules -->
    <div class="ds-grid-2">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:var(--weight-bold);color:var(--color-success);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-wide);margin-bottom:var(--space-4)">✓ DO — Always</h3>
        <ul class="rule-list">
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Lead with the user's pain or transformation — not what the product does</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Use short, punchy sentences. Sub-12 words for H1 where possible</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Use blue accent to emphasise the most powerful phrase on the page</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Write the headline last — after you know what the product actually does</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Sub-headline should explain HOW, not repeat WHAT</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon do">✓</div><div class="rule-text">Test at least 3 headline variants before shipping</div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:var(--weight-bold);color:var(--color-error);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-wide);margin-bottom:var(--space-4)">✗ DON'T — Never</h3>
        <ul class="rule-list">
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't start with "We are" or "Introducing" — nobody cares yet</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't use adjectives like "seamless", "robust", or "powerful"</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't put a feature list in the headline — that's what the body is for</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't use more than 2 font sizes in a single headline block</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't centre-align body text — only headlines and short CTAs</div></li>
          <li class="rule-item"><div class="rule-icon dont">✗</div><div class="rule-text">Don't use all-caps in H1 — only overlines and labels</div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tone -->
    <div class="ds-divider"></div>
    <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:var(--weight-bold);color:var(--ink-500);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:var(--tracking-wide);margin-bottom:var(--space-4)">Brand Voice</h3>
    <div class="ds-grid-4">
      <div class="ds-card-surface" style="text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">⚡</div>
        <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);margin-bottom:4px">Direct</div>
        <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-500)">Say it in half the words. Cut every hedge.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-card-surface" style="text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">🎯</div>
        <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);margin-bottom:4px">Outcome-first</div>
        <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-500)">Lead with what the user gains. Features explain how.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-card-surface" style="text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">🔬</div>
        <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);margin-bottom:4px">Precise</div>
        <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-500)">"60 seconds" beats "quickly". Specific wins.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-card-surface" style="text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:var(--space-2)">🤝</div>
        <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ink-900);margin-bottom:4px">Human</div>
        <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--ink-500)">Technical products, non-technical copy. Respect the reader.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

